These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, dancer, scientist
1. the dancer is on the far left##1
2. the police-officer is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | dancer | scientist | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, freelancer, paramedic
1. the paramedic is on the far right##1
2. the project-manager is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | project-manager | freelancer | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, cooking, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | cooking | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, thai, british
1. the thai is on the far right##1
2. the thai is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | canadian | british | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, juice
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | fanta | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, trike
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | trike | jet-ski | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, romance, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | satire | romance |

 #################################

 
